OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe evening
OL,6,Fwill start off quite cloudy, and then
OL,7,Fsee some bright spells and showers.
OL,8,FThese showers will clear form the late
OL,9,Fevening and clear spells will increase
OL,10,Ftowards the morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FThe morning will be mostly dry
OL,13,Fwith bright or sunny spells, a few
OL,14,Fshowers in the northwest. Scattered
OL,15,Fshowers build in the afternoon and
OL,16,Fcloud increases towards the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
