OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,FSaturday morning with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain, some heavy, turning showery
OL,8,Flater. Further showery rain Sunday,
OL,9,Fheavy for a time. Rain clears Monday
OL,10,Fmorning, then bright spells and some
OL,11,Fshowers.
